name: Kayns Room MAIDS OF LEGENDS 2020
description:
Pre warning okay, this is pretty janky.

If you're seeing this then you're probably fresh off the heels of the Maids of Legends Haunted House Event!! Thank you so much for participating in Kayns room, it was a lot of hard work to pull off since I had to draw AND code everything myself this time in the span of a week ;; 

There's other dialogue that wasn't shown in the MoL posts so I wanted to upload the whole project here so you can read through it in your own time!

If you haven't come here from the Maids of Legends RP twitter then... This will look pretty weird to you. Just treat it as a weird practise project! Since that's basically what this was.

Art @ Salty Schnecke
Coding @ Salty Schnecke
RP Event @ Maids of Legends
